Text.string: I smell a conflagration on the wind.
I'll give your pets a good home at the station.
You're just fuel for the fire, baby.
You've got arsonist written aaaall over you!
Aw, it's getting hot in here!
I know a firebug when I see one!
Looks like you got a burn notice.
Come on, baby! Light my fire!
You look like fire to me.
Remember, only you can prevent-- ah, forget it.
Guess it's time for a break.
Make like a banana and TURN BROWN REAL FAST!
I axe at a twelfth-grade level!
I was literally made for this!
Try using fire! That I can work with.
I'd like to see that burn down.
What are we supposed to do with that?
You'll get frosted for that, prick!
The flame that burns twice as bright...
That was my friend, damn it!
It takes fire to make fire.
Fire in the hole! But not for long.
Now what will I throw in the air to affirm that I am indeed a true player?
I'm no teacher, but I'll take you to school.
You better check yourself before I wreck you myself.
Oh, I KNOW you ain't flexin' to ME.
And that's the end of that chapter...
You ain't fire. You're lukewarm at best.
No, not today. Not even this week.
I'm gonna take your face -- off.
Someone's got a fire in their belly!
Burning like the surface of a sun!
Don't you hit me back now!
